Class JoxyFileChooserUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI
      • javax.swing.plaf.FileChooserUI
        • javax.swing.plaf.basic.BasicFileChooserUI
          • javax.swing.plaf.metal.MetalFileChooserUI
            • joxy.JoxyFileChooserUI

  • public class JoxyFileChooserUI
extends MetalFileChooserUI
    Joxy's UI delegate for the JFileChooser.

    We extend Metal's file chooser here, because the basic LAF file chooser does nothing. However we want to use a real native file chooser in the future.

    Author:
    Thom Castermans, Willem Sonke
